image_analysis.description: A high-angle photograph of a lavishly decorated interior living room or salon. The room features orange walls, an ornate white coffered ceiling, and large windows with cream-colored curtains featuring a Greek key border. Furniture includes a teal velvet sofa, black and white armchairs, and several ornate side tables. A large abstract painting with a blue background and a central dark figure hangs on the wall. The floor is covered by a large, colorful geometric rug with yellow, teal, and purple patterns. Several lamps with pleated shades are visible, providing warm lighting.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room view showing furniture arrangement, wall decor, and architectural details.
